COMPONENT	DATAELEMENT	DATATYPE	LENGTH	DECIMALS	DESCRIPTION
PNAME	RS38L_PAR_				Parameter name
PSEQ	INT4				Chunk sequence (1-based) - PVALUE chunks reassembled in PSEQ order per PNAME
PTYPE	CHAR1				Parameter type: I=Importing E=Exporting C=Changing T=Tables
PTYPENAME	DDOBJNAME				ABAP Dictionary type name (e.g. PROGNAME, BAPI_RETURN, ABAPTXT255_TAB)
PVALUE	ZCMDE_RFCVAL				asXML payload chunk (CALL TRANSFORMATION id) - CHAR 1333 via custom DE ZCMDE_RFCVAL on domain ZCMD_RFCVAL